ence\": \"She feared deportation back to Cameroon, where a return would be unsafe due to her sexuality as homosexuality is illegal there.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 846, \"end\": 854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.998108739506607, \"rank\": 0.0011219662215902774, \"text\": \"Cameroon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cameroon_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deportation\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"a return\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"her sexuality\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"homosexuality\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An energetic start to the bout saw Ngamba clipped by Bylon a couple of times and although the refugee fighter grew into the round, she struggled to land her punches and the first round went unanimously to thePanamaboxer.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"score\": 0.9999749969287564, \"rank\": 2.4952844783282893e-05, \"text\": \"Ngamba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An energetic start\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"Bylon\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"the refugee fighter\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"the round\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"her punches\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1128}, {\"ngram\": \"thePanamaboxer\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The